import React from "react";
import ReactDOM from "react-dom";
import "./index.css";
//import * as serviceWorker from "./serviceWorker";
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Routes } from "react-router-dom";
import {
  Navigation,
  Footer,
  Home,
  Trailmap,
  Contact,
  Notes,
  Socials,
  Hexial,
  Hexq1,
  Hexq2,
  Hexq3,
  Hexwin,
  Hexgameover,
  Blog,
  Posts,
  Post,
} from "./components";

import { ProSidebar, Menu, MenuItem, SubMenu } from 'react-pro-sidebar';
import 'react-pro-sidebar/dist/css/styles.css';
import Logo from '../assets/logo192.png';

ProSidebar.render(
<ProSidebar>
  <Menu iconShape="square">
    <MenuItem icon={<Logo />}>Dashboard</MenuItem>
    <SubMenu title="Components" icon={<Logo />}>
      <MenuItem>Component 1</MenuItem>
      <MenuItem>Component 2</MenuItem>
    </SubMenu>
  </Menu>
</ProSidebar>
);

ReactDOM.render(
  <Router>
    <Navigation />
    <Routes>
      <Route path="/" element={<Home />} />
      <Route path="/trailmap" element={<Trailmap />} />
      <Route path="/contact" element={<Contact />} />
      <Route path="/notes" element={<Notes />} />
      <Route path="/socials" element={<Socials />} />
      <Route path="/hexial" element={<Hexial />} />
      <Route path="/hexq1" element={<Hexq1 />} />
      <Route path="/hexq2" element={<Hexq2 />} />
      <Route path="/hexq3" element={<Hexq3 />} />
      <Route path="/hexwin" element={<Hexwin />} />
      <Route path="/hexgameover" element={<Hexgameover />} />
      <Route path="/blog" element={<Blog />}>
        <Route path="" element={<Posts />} />
        <Route path=":postSlug" element={<Post />} />
      </Route>
    </Routes>
    <Footer />
  </Router>,

  document.getElementById("root")
);

//serviceWorker.unregister();
